OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772118239
OL,3,CFifa will allow Scotland fans to wear
OL,4,Ctheir sporrans at the World Cup
OL,6,FFans supporting Scotland at the 2026
OL,7,FWorld Cup will be allowed to wear
OL,8,Ftheir sporrans at matches, Fifa has
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FStrict tournament bag restrictions,
OL,12,Fonly accepting smaller bags into
OL,13,Fvenues, left supporters concerned that
OL,14,Ftheir sporrans would not meet the
OL,15,Fcriteria.
OL,17,FHowever, talks between Fifa and the
OL,18,FScottish Football Association
OL,19,Fconcluded that sporrans, traditional
OL,20,Fpouches worn by Scots over their
OL,21,Fkilts, would be allowed in the crowd.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
