FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772118239
OL,3,CFifa will allow Scotland fans to wear
OL,4,Ctheir sporrans at the World Cup
OL,6,FA SFA spokesperson said: "FIFA have
OL,7,Fconfirmed that sporrans will be
OL,8,Fpermitted into the stadiums following
OL,9,Fthe standard search and inspection
OL,10,Fprocedures and will continue to work
OL,11,Ftogether with the Scottish FA to
OL,12,Feducate their matchday staff as they
OL,13,Fprepare to welcome fans to Boston and
OL,14,FMiami.
OL,16,F"The ticketing and membership team at
OL,17,Fthe Scottish FA are in continued
OL,18,Fdialogue with the tournament hosts to
OL,19,Fensure that the Scotland fans will be
OL,20,Fwelcomed to venues in the way they
OL,21,Fhave been across the world."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
