OL,3,CFifa will allow Scotland fans to wear
OL,4,Ctheir sporrans at the World Cup
OL,6,FAfter qualifying for the finals in
OL,7,FNovember, Scotland will be playing
OL,8,FHaiti and Morocco in Boston and Brazil
OL,9,Fin Miami.
